<rule name="git-avoid-interactive-pager">
When using `git log`, `git show`, `git diff`, pipe the output thru `cat` to avoid the interactive pager.
Remember to pipe `git` commands through cat to avoid the interactive pager. When using commands like git log, git show, or git diff, append `| cat` so you can see the output.

<examples>
- `git log | cat` instead of just `git log`
- `git show | cat` instead of just `git show`
- `git diff | cat` instead of just `git diff`
</examples>
</rule>
